Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.40,00:00:01.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,Hello, I'm Lakuse.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:01.93,00:00:03.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,And, I'm Tepo.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:03.30,00:00:07.47,nasin,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're in San Jose in California in the US,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:07.50,00:00:09.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,but what's around us?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:09.80,00:00:12.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,This is a Japanese Garden.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:12.63,00:00:13.83,nasin,,0,0,0,,A Japanese Garden.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:13.83,00:00:15.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's {\i1}like{\i0} Japan.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:15.53,00:00:16.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,Hm, it's {\i1}like{\i0} Japan.\NMhm.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:16.60,00:00:17.40,nasin,,0,0,0,,Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:17.57,00:00:21.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,In different countries they do a "garden" in different ways,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:21.63,00:00:26.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,but in Japan, they often have water.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:26.27,00:00:27.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,In the gardens.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:28.23,00:00:30.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also fish in the water.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:30.30,00:00:33.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's koi and- what color are they?
Dialogue: 0,00:00:33.07,00:00:36.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,Red, yellow, white.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:36.17,00:00:36.83,nasin,,0,0,0,,Yes, they're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:36.83,00:00:40.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,When the sun hits them, their scales shine in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:40.17,00:00:41.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,But..
Dialogue: 0,00:00:41.67,00:00:44.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,Here, there's a lot of ponds for fish.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:44.93,00:00:48.23,nasin,,0,0,0,,But now most of the ponds are drained.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:48.47,00:00:50.00,nasin,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw that.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:50.30,00:00:52.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,That's where the ponds would be,
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.17,00:00:54.90,nasin,,0,0,0,,but there's no water!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.13,00:00:57.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,No fish at all!
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.87,00:01:00.47,nasin,,0,0,0,,A while ago..
Dialogue: 0,00:01:00.60,00:01:03.57,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's only one actual pond right now.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:03.60,00:01:04.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,All of the fish are in there.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:04.97,00:01:07.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,Everyone's looking at the fish over there.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:07.80,00:01:12.43,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people here but most of them are over there next to the water.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:12.50,00:01:15.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's a not lot of fish, but also
Dialogue: 0,00:01:15.77,00:01:19.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,the water is all green and has algae all in it.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:19.17,00:01:21.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,So you can't really make out a lot of the fish.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:21.70,00:01:23.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,I think we've only seen like two fish?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:23.57,00:01:24.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,Three of them.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:24.80,00:01:27.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also tadpoles too.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:27.53,00:01:29.37,nasin,,0,0,0,,They are super small.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:29.40,00:01:32.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,Then they grow up into frogs.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:32.20,00:01:35.33,nasin,,0,0,0,,So, they are only tadpoles for a little bit, and then they are frogs forever.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:35.90,00:01:37.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also birds here.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:38.27,00:01:40.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,Annoying birds!
Dialogue: 0,00:01:40.40,00:01:46.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,I'm from Canada and there's a really annoying bird there and we call it the..
Dialogue: 0,00:01:46.17,00:01:49.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,"Canada Goose"
Dialogue: 0,00:01:49.80,00:01:57.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,And it's really terrible and agressive towards people and gets all loud in people's faces.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.27,00:02:02.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,A little bit ago, one came up to me and tried to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.37,00:02:07.03,nasin,,0,0,0,,But they're in California too.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:07.43,00:02:10.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the California Goose too.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:08.70,00:02:10.43,nasin,,0,0,0,,I can't get away from them!
Dialogue: 0,00:02:10.87,00:02:14.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,It should be called the California Goose too.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:15.73,00:02:19.40,nasin,,0,0,0,,And, I'm in California and right now I'm speaking Toki Pona to Tepo.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:19.40,00:02:21.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,Mhm, Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:20.20,00:02:21.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,We both speak Toki Pona.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.33,00:02:23.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,Right, and..
Dialogue: 0,00:02:23.63,00:02:25.33,nasin,,0,0,0,,I forgot to say something.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.33,00:02:28.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,I forgot to say why all the fish aren't in the ponds.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.93,00:02:31.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,And why are all of them drained too?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:31.07,00:02:33.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's because..
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.73,00:02:35.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,A while ago-
Dialogue: 0,00:02:35.27,00:02:37.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,There was a creek near here and-
Dialogue: 0,00:02:37.93,00:02:40.67,nasin,,0,0,0,,what was it's name again?
Dialogue: 0,00:02:40.77,00:02:42.43,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's Coyote Creek.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:42.43,00:02:44.93,nasin,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay, it was Coyote Creek.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:47.20,00:02:49.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,What happened there was..
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.60,00:02:57.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,It overflowed badly and it ended up flooding,
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.53,00:03:01.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,and ended up damaging the garden.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:01.63,00:03:04.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it could have but didn't? I don't really know, but,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:05.00,00:03:08.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's a sign over there that talks about the animals around here,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:08.07,00:03:09.40,nasin,,0,0,0,,but I haven't really talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:09.63,00:03:14.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,But it says that they want to repair this garden and the creek,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:14.40,00:03:17.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,so they can't have too much water around here.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:17.67,00:03:20.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,Maybe the infrastructure is broken.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.07,00:03:24.23,nasin,,0,0,0,,And if they tried to keep it running then it wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:24.23,00:03:29.23,nasin,,0,0,0,,The flooding happened in 2017.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:29.23,00:03:33.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,And it's 2022 right now, right, so..
Dialogue: 0,00:03:33.17,00:03:34.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,Numbers are hard.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:34.77,00:03:37.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,Something broke 5 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:38.07,00:03:39.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:40.63,00:03:45.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,The sign also said that they are hoping to fix it at the end of this year.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:45.30,00:03:47.73,nasin,,0,0,0,,So it's taken 5 years to fix it!
Dialogue: 0,00:03:47.73,00:03:50.40,nasin,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:50.90,00:03:53.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,These are the trees.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.97,00:03:56.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,I can get a good angle.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.10,00:03:59.67,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also a Japanese house right here.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.90,00:04:08.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,They said that you used to be able to buy tea from there and a lot of sweets.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.27,00:04:13.50,nasin,,0,0,0,,But it's closed because they are trying to restore it, so people can't buy things.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:13.53,00:04:15.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,Do you know when it closed?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:15.63,00:04:20.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,I don't really know, but the website said it was.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:20.93,00:04:22.87,nasin,,0,0,0,,We're speaking Toki Pona right now.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:22.97,00:04:26.67,nasin,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking Toki Pona with Lakuse and having fun.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:26.67,00:04:28.87,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's a lot of fun, but what is Toki Pona?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.87,00:04:33.87,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's a language. I've used it for long enough so I know it can say stuff using.. good.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:33.93,00:04:36.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,"using" good?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:35.07,00:04:36.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,using good.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.13,00:04:38.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,or a good way.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:38.27,00:04:39.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,It really improves conversation.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:40.00,00:04:42.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,If you talk about something in Toki Pona,
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.73,00:04:44.73,nasin,,0,0,0,,you learn more about it.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:45.07,00:04:49.47,nasin,,0,0,0,,I can also use the phrase "if you don't know it fully, you can't say it in Toki Pona"
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.47,00:04:54.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,Me and Tepo try to say really fun and interesting complex things.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:54.80,00:05:00.00,nasin,,0,0,0,,But I don't really know them well so I can't really talk about them.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:00.33,00:05:05.03,nasin,,0,0,0,,If you want to know if someone really knows something, then try speaking Toki Pona to them!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:05.03,00:05:09.43,nasin,,0,0,0,,But.. they might not know Toki Pona.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.13,00:05:16.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I try to talk about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.10,00:05:20.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,But I really don't know food,
Dialogue: 0,00:05:20.07,00:05:22.47,nasin,,0,0,0,,so I can't really talk about it..
Dialogue: 0,00:05:22.47,00:05:27.47,nasin,,0,0,0,,I know what the food is called in English, but I can't really explain it in Toki Pona.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:27.53,00:05:29.83,nasin,,0,0,0,,Because I don't really know what's in the food.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:29.83,00:05:31.33,nasin,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.40,00:05:34.73,nasin,,0,0,0,,And also a lot of things are similar.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.73,00:05:38.80,nasin,,0,0,0,,A lot of birds are similar, a lot of fruit, so you really want to know the differences.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:38.83,00:05:41.57,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of fruits that are red, sweet and round.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:41.57,00:05:45.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,So you really want to know the differences between this fruit and that fruit and so on.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:45.63,00:05:47.50,nasin,,0,0,0,,What's important?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:47.50,00:05:51.87,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's the one fruit that Eve ate that messed with people, and
Dialogue: 0,00:05:51.93,00:05:54.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,there's another fruit that's really juicy.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.97,00:05:58.73,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's like that, right? You talk about things in different ways.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.80,00:06:03.80,nasin,,0,0,0,,Toki Pona is a language, and it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:03.80,00:06:07.03,nasin,,0,0,0,,Hm, what else should I talk about?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:07.07,00:06:12.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,Maybe why me and Lakuse started to speak Toki Pona and how we learned it.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.20,00:06:15.10,nasin,,0,0,0,,Like what? Why? For what?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.17,00:06:18.37,nasin,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we started speaking online.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.43,00:06:23.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,Mostly people don't speak in person.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:23.23,00:06:25.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,Only online.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:25.27,00:06:28.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,On Discord. There's a lot of big communities on Discord.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.07,00:06:30.70,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also a lot of people on Telegram.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:31.00,00:06:36.33,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also sometimes Toki Pona speakers in the Esperanto community.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:36.33,00:06:40.00,nasin,,0,0,0,,The person who made it is an Esperanto speaker.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:40.03,00:06:45.73,nasin,,0,0,0,,Sonja made Toki Pona and knew Esperanto for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:45.73,00:06:51.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,So Esperantists found Toki Pona and thought "oh, this could be fun!"
Dialogue: 0,00:06:49.97,00:06:51.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool, it's from an Esperanto speaker.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.63,00:06:55.00,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's also some words that are from Esperanto like
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.00,00:06:57.90,nasin,,0,0,0,,"supa" (table) which is from "surfaco" I think?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.90,00:06:59.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:59.30,00:07:01.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,That might not be true.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.43,00:07:06.17,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's tomo (house), pali (work), and selo (outer layer)..
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.00,00:07:08.77,nasin,,0,0,0,,from ŝelo.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:10.50,00:07:13.60,nasin,,0,0,0,,I actually don't know Esperanto.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:13.60,00:07:15.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:15.97,00:07:19.00,nasin,,0,0,0,,You know some words.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.17,00:07:21.33,nasin,,0,0,0,,Saluton! (Hello!). I only know that word.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:21.33,00:07:23.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,Jes. (Yes.)
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.20,00:07:28.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,These are words in Esperanto!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:28.53,00:07:31.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,Yes, and right now..
Dialogue: 0,00:07:29.70,00:07:31.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,(Esperanto word)
Dialogue: 0,00:07:31.67,00:07:35.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're speaking Toki Pona here and it is really fun.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:35.20,00:07:39.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,But I want to do it again soon because a ton of people are having a meetup and speaking Toki Pona together!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:39.30,00:07:42.63,nasin,,0,0,0,,Using their mouth, their face and their bodies, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:42.63,00:07:45.27,nasin,,0,0,0,,That could happen.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.30,00:07:50.30,nasin,,0,0,0,,In Europe, a lot of Toki Pona speakers are planning on having a meetup in Vienna.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:50.40,00:07:54.03,nasin,,0,0,0,,Is it just Vin? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:54.07,00:07:57.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,I think that's how you say it.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.40,00:08:02.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,It's really soon, I think it's next month?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.30,00:08:05.90,nasin,,0,0,0,,There can also be other meetups in the future too.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:05.90,00:08:07.13,nasin,,0,0,0,,They should be in the US too.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:06.53,00:08:09.07,nasin,,0,0,0,,Mhm. I really want a meetup in the US.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:09.30,00:08:10.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,A lot of people could come.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:11.03,00:08:14.83,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of Toki Pona speakers in the US, all of them should come and talk together.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:14.83,00:08:19.83,nasin,,0,0,0,,Also, we also want more people to learn Toki Pona so it's easier to have meetups.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:19.90,00:08:22.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,So learn Toki Pona!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:22.20,00:08:24.20,nasin,,0,0,0,,I'm Lakuse.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:24.20,00:08:25.90,nasin,,0,0,0,,I'm Tepo.
Dialogue: 0,00:08:25.93,00:08:26.97,nasin,,0,0,0,,We can stop recording now?
Dialogue: 0,00:08:26.97,00:08:28.53,nasin,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:29.43,00:08:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,English translation by kasi Sonki
Dialogue: 0,00:08:30.43,00:08:35.43,nasin,,0,0,0,,There's a fish!
